edu.snu.coral.common.ir.vertex.transform

Interface Transform<I,O>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - input type.
    O - output type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CollectTransform, CreateViewTransform, DoTransform, EmptyComponents.EmptyTransform, FlatMapTransform, FlattenTransform, GroupByKeyTransform, GroupByKeyTransform, MapToPairTransform, MapTransform, ReduceByKeyTransform, ReduceTransform, RelayTransform, WindowTransform

    public interface Transform<I,O>
extends Serializable
    Interface for specifying 'What' to do with data. It is to be implemented in the compiler frontend, possibly for every operator in a dataflow language. 'How' and 'When' to do with its input/output data are up to the runtime.
